span.span: Use this class only when you have to access an earlier event in this class that has been subsequently extended in a later version of Outlook.

summary.span: Sinon, utilisez l’interface .NET dérivée de la coclasse COM.

span.span: Otherwise, use the .NET interface derived from the COM coclass.
